* Palace Master Shrine: {{ill|Ashinazuchi and Tenazuchi|ja|アシナヅチ・テナヅチ|lt=Ashinazuchi, Tenazuchi|lt_ja=足名稚命、手名稚命|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Three Shrines (Sanjagu):
** {{ill|Amaterasu Ōmikami Shrine|ja|天照大神|1=Amaterasu|lt=Amaterasu Ōmikami|12=draft|12=draft}} 
** {{ill|Tsukuyomi Shrine|ja|ツクヨミ|lt=Tsukuyomi, Great Deity|lt_ja=月讀大神|12=draft|12=draft}}
** {{ill|Hiruko Shrine|ja|Hiruko|lt=Hiruko|lt_ja=蛭子神|12=draft|12=draft}}
* Itsukushima Shrine: {{ill|Ichikishimahime Shrine|ja|イチキシマヒメ|lt=Ichikishimahime|lt_ja=市杵嶌姫命|12=draft|12=draft}}

==行事==
