* Palace Master Shrine: {{ill|Ashinazuchi and Tenazuchi|ja|アシナヅチ・テナヅチ|lt=Ashinazuchi, Tenazuchi|lt_ja=足名稚命、手名稚命|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
* Three Shrines (Sanjagu):
