{{Shrine
|Name = Sakatoke Shrine
|Religious_affiliation = {{ill|Shinto|ja|神道|qq=draft|qq=draft}}
|Location = Kyoto Prefecture, {{ill|Otokun District|ja|乙訓郡|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, {{ill|Ōyamazaki Town|ja|大山崎町|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, Ōyamazaki Tenno 46
