** {{ill|Hiruko Shrine|ja|Hiruko|lt=Hiruko|lt_ja=蛭子神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiruko Shrine|qq=}}
* Itsukushima Shrine: {{ill|Ichikishima-hime Shrine|ja|イチキシマヒメ|1=Ichikishima-hime|lt=Ichikishima-hime|lt=Ichikishima-hime|lt_ja=市杵嶌姫命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime Shrine|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime|qq=}}

