==摂末社== * Guardian Shrine: [[:en:Ōkuninushi|Ōkuninushi]] * Palace Master Shrine: [[:en:Ashinazuchi and Tenazuchi|Ashinazuchi, Tenazuchi]] * Three Shrines (Sanjagu): ** [[:en:Amaterasu|Amaterasu Ōmikami]] ** [[:en:Tsukuyomi-no-Mikoto|Tsukuyomi, Great Deity]] ** {{ill|Hiruko Shrine|ja|Hiruko|lt=Hiruko|lt_ja=蛭子神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiruko Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * Itsukushima Shrine: {{ill|Ichikishima-hime Shrine|ja|イチキシマヒメ|1=Ichikishima-hime|lt=Ichikishima-hime|lt=Ichikishima-hime|lt_ja=市杵嶌姫命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime Shrine|13=User:Immanuelle/Ichikishima-hime|qq=}}
